{
  "video_id": "iEy-xTbcr2A",
  "title": "America's forgotten working class | J.D. Vance",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12880.0,
      "end_time": 15719.0,
      "text": "I remember the very first time I went to a nice restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15719.0,
      "end_time": 17360.0,
      "text": "a really nice restaurant."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17360.0,
      "end_time": 19520.0,
      "text": "It was for a law firm recruitment dinner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19520.0,
      "end_time": 22000.0,
      "text": "and I remember beforehand the waitress walked around"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22000.0,
      "end_time": 23880.0,
      "text": "and asked whether we wanted some wine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23880.0,
      "end_time": 26800.0,
      "text": "so I said, &quot;Sure, I&#39;ll take some white wine.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26800.0,
      "end_time": 28560.0,
      "text": "And she immediately said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28560.0,
      "end_time": 31680.0,
      "text": "&quot;Would you like sauvignon blanc or chardonnay?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31680.0,
      "end_time": 33640.0,
      "text": "And I remember thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33640.0,
      "end_time": 36520.0,
      "text": "&quot;Come on, lady, stop with the fancy French words"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36520.0,
      "end_time": 39400.0,
      "text": "and just give me some white wine.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39400.0,
      "end_time": 41040.0,
      "text": "But I used my powers of deduction"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41040.0,
      "end_time": 43480.0,
      "text": "and recognized that chardonnay and sauvignon blanc"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43480.0,
      "end_time": 45400.0,
      "text": "were two separate types of white wine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45400.0,
      "end_time": 47840.0,
      "text": "and so I told her that I would take the chardonnay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47840.0,
      "end_time": 51960.0,
      "text": "because frankly that was the easiest one to pronounce for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51960.0,
      "end_time": 54080.0,
      "text": "So I had a lot of experiences like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54080.0,
      "end_time": 57480.0,
      "text": "during my first couple of years as a law student at Yale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57480.0,
      "end_time": 61240.0,
      "text": "because, despite all outward appearances, I&#39;m a cultural outsider."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61240.0,
      "end_time": 62840.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t come from the elites."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62840.0,
      "end_time": 67200.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t come from the Northeast or from San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67200.0,
      "end_time": 69320.0,
      "text": "I came from a southern Ohio steel town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69320.0,
      "end_time": 72080.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a town that&#39;s really struggling in a lot of ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72080.0,
      "end_time": 74560.0,
      "text": "ways that are indicative of the broader struggles"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74560.0,
      "end_time": 76720.0,
      "text": "of America&#39;s working class."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76720.0,
      "end_time": 78080.0,
      "text": "Heroin has moved in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78080.0,
      "end_time": 80680.0,
      "text": "killing a lot of people, people I know."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80680.0,
      "end_time": 85400.0,
      "text": "Family violence, domestic violence, and divorce have torn apart families."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 89600.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s a very unique sense of pessimism that&#39;s moved in."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89600.0,
      "end_time": 92240.0,
      "text": "Think about rising mortality rates in these communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92240.0,
      "end_time": 94440.0,
      "text": "and recognize that for a lot of these folks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94440.0,
      "end_time": 96040.0,
      "text": "the problems that they&#39;re seeing"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96040.0,
      "end_time": 99760.0,
      "text": "are actually causing rising death rates in their own communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99760.0,
      "end_time": 103160.0,
      "text": "so there&#39;s a very real sense of struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103160.0,
      "end_time": 105720.0,
      "text": "I had a very front-row seat to that struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105720.0,
      "end_time": 111080.0,
      "text": "My family has been part of that struggle for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111080.0,
      "end_time": 115440.0,
      "text": "I come from a family that doesn&#39;t have a whole lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115440.0,
      "end_time": 117880.0,
      "text": "The addiction that plagued my community"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117880.0,
      "end_time": 121760.0,
      "text": "also plagued my family, and even, sadly, my own mom."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121760.0,
      "end_time": 125920.0,
      "text": "There were a lot of problems that I saw in my own family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125920.0,
      "end_time": 128800.0,
      "text": "problems caused sometimes by a lack of money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "problems caused sometimes by a lack of access to resources and social capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133160.0,
      "end_time": 136400.0,
      "text": "that really affected my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136400.0,
      "end_time": 139200.0,
      "text": "If you had looked at my life when I was 14 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139200.0,
      "end_time": 142280.0,
      "text": "and said, &quot;Well, what&#39;s going to happen to this kid?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142280.0,
      "end_time": 145160.0,
      "text": "you would have concluded that I would have struggled"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 148560.0,
      "text": "with what academics call upward mobility."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148560.0,
      "end_time": 151560.0,
      "text": "So upward mobility is an abstract term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151560.0,
      "end_time": 154320.0,
      "text": "but it strikes at something that&#39;s very core"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 154320.0,
      "end_time": 156040.0,
      "text": "at the heart of the American Dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156040.0,
      "end_time": 157280.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157280.0,
      "end_time": 159080.0,
      "text": "and it measures whether kids like me"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159080.0,
      "end_time": 162120.0,
      "text": "who grow up in poor communities are going to live a better life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162120.0,
      "end_time": 167520.0,
      "text": "whether they&#39;re going to have a chance to live a materially better existence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167520.0,
      "end_time": 171080.0,
      "text": "or whether they&#39;re going to stay in the circumstances where they came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171080.0,
      "end_time": 173520.0,
      "text": "And one of the things we&#39;ve learned, unfortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 173520.0,
      "end_time": 177480.0,
      "text": "is that upward mobility isn&#39;t as high as we&#39;d like it to be in this country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 177480.0,
      "end_time": 182080.0,
      "text": "and interestingly, it&#39;s very geographically distributed."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182080.0,
      "end_time": 184840.0,
      "text": "So take Utah, for instance."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184840.0,
      "end_time": 188400.0,
      "text": "In Utah a poor kid is actually doing OK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188400.0,
      "end_time": 192560.0,
      "text": "very likely to live their share and their part in the American Dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192560.0,
      "end_time": 194440.0,
      "text": "But if you think of where I&#39;m from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194440.0,
      "end_time": 198400.0,
      "text": "in the South, in Appalachia, in southern Ohio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 198400.0,
      "end_time": 202640.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s very unlikely that kids like that will rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202640.0,
      "end_time": 204920.0,
      "text": "The American Dream in those parts of the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204920.0,
      "end_time": 207960.0,
      "text": "is in a very real sense just a dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 207960.0,
      "end_time": 210120.0,
      "text": "So why is that happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 210120.0,
      "end_time": 212960.0,
      "text": "So one reason is obviously economic or structural."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 212960.0,
      "end_time": 214520.0,
      "text": "So you think of these areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 214520.0,
      "end_time": 217160.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re beset by these terrible economic trends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 219800.0,
      "text": "built around industries like coal and steel"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219800.0,
      "end_time": 222320.0,
      "text": "that make it harder for folks to get ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222320.0,
      "end_time": 223920.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s certainly one problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 223920.0,
      "end_time": 227440.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s also the problem of brain drain, where the really talented people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227440.0,
      "end_time": 229840.0,
      "text": "because they can&#39;t find high-skilled work at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 229840.0,
      "end_time": 231120.0,
      "text": "end up moving elsewhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 231120.0,
      "end_time": 234160.0,
      "text": "so they don&#39;t build a business or non-profit where they&#39;re from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234160.0,
      "end_time": 237160.0,
      "text": "they end up going elsewhere and taking their talents with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 237160.0,
      "end_time": 239840.0,
      "text": "There are failing schools in a lot of these communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239840.0,
      "end_time": 241920.0,
      "text": "failing to give kids the educational leg up"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241920.0,
      "end_time": 245480.0,
      "text": "that really makes it possible for kids to have opportunities later in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 245480.0,
      "end_time": 247040.0,
      "text": "These things are all important."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 247040.0,
      "end_time": 249480.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean to discount these structural barriers."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 249480.0,
      "end_time": 251840.0,
      "text": "But when I look back at my life and my community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 251840.0,
      "end_time": 255840.0,
      "text": "something else was going on, something else mattered."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 255840.0,
      "end_time": 260120.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s difficult to quantify, but it was no less real."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 260120.0,
      "end_time": 263800.0,
      "text": "So for starters, there was a very real sense of hopelessness"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 263800.0,
      "end_time": 265600.0,
      "text": "in the community that I grew up in."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 265600.0,
      "end_time": 268760.0,
      "text": "There was a sense that kids had that their choices didn&#39;t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 268760.0,
      "end_time": 271440.0,
      "text": "No matter what happened, no matter how hard they worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 271440.0,
      "end_time": 273560.0,
      "text": "no matter how hard they tried to get ahead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 273560.0,
      "end_time": 276160.0,
      "text": "nothing good would happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 276160.0,
      "end_time": 279240.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s a tough feeling to grow up around."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 279240.0,
      "end_time": 282440.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a tough mindset to penetrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 282440.0,
      "end_time": 287240.0,
      "text": "and it leads sometimes to very conspiratorial places."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 287240.0,
      "end_time": 291200.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s just take one political issue that&#39;s pretty hot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 291200.0,
      "end_time": 292720.0,
      "text": "affirmative action."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 292720.0,
      "end_time": 296040.0,
      "text": "So depending on your politics, you might think that affirmative action"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 296040.0,
      "end_time": 299440.0,
      "text": "is either a wise or an unwise way to promote diversity in the workplace"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 300760.0,
      "text": "or the classroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 300760.0,
      "end_time": 302800.0,
      "text": "But if you grow up in an area like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 302800.0,
      "end_time": 306560.0,
      "text": "you see affirmative action as a tool to hold people like you back."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 306560.0,
      "end_time": 309840.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s especially true if you&#39;re a member of the white working class."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 309840.0,
      "end_time": 313280.0,
      "text": "You see it as something that isn&#39;t just about good or bad policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 313280.0,
      "end_time": 316000.0,
      "text": "You see it as something that&#39;s actively conspiring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 316000.0,
      "end_time": 318280.0,
      "text": "where people with political and financial power"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 318280.0,
      "end_time": 319920.0,
      "text": "are working against you."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 319920.0,
      "end_time": 325520.0,
      "text": "And there are a lot of ways that you see that conspiracy against you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 325520.0,
      "end_time": 328440.0,
      "text": "perceived, real, but it&#39;s there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 328440.0,
      "end_time": 331040.0,
      "text": "and it warps expectations."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 331040.0,
      "end_time": 334280.0,
      "text": "So if you think about what do you do when you grow up in that world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 334280.0,
      "end_time": 336040.0,
      "text": "you can respond in a couple of ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 336040.0,
      "end_time": 338240.0,
      "text": "One, you can say, &quot;I&#39;m not going to work hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 338240.0,
      "end_time": 341160.0,
      "text": "because no matter how hard I work, it&#39;s not going to matter.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 341160.0,
      "end_time": 342840.0,
      "text": "Another thing you might do is say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 342840.0,
      "end_time": 346080.0,
      "text": "&quot;Well, I&#39;m not going to go after the traditional markers of success,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 346080.0,
      "end_time": 348440.0,
      "text": "like a university education or a prestigious job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 348440.0,
      "end_time": 351360.0,
      "text": "because the people who care about those things are unlike me."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 351360.0,
      "end_time": 353004.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re never going to let me in.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 353004.0,
      "end_time": 355505.0,
      "text": "When I got admitted to Yale, a family member asked me"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 355505.0,
      "end_time": 358840.0,
      "text": "if I had pretended to be a liberal to get by the admissions committee."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 358840.0,
      "end_time": 360640.0,
      "text": "Seriously."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 360640.0,
      "end_time": 364680.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s obviously not the case that there was a liberal box to check"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 364680.0,
      "end_time": 366200.0,
      "text": "on the application,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 366200.0,
      "end_time": 369880.0,
      "text": "but it speaks to a very real insecurity in these places"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 369880.0,
      "end_time": 372280.0,
      "text": "that you have to pretend to be somebody you&#39;re not"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 372280.0,
      "end_time": 375080.0,
      "text": "to get past these various social barriers."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 375080.0,
      "end_time": 377640.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very significant problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377640.0,
      "end_time": 380080.0,
      "text": "Even if you don&#39;t give in to that hopelessness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 380080.0,
      "end_time": 381920.0,
      "text": "even if you think, let&#39;s say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 381920.0,
      "end_time": 385560.0,
      "text": "that your choices matter and you want to make the good choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 385560.0,
      "end_time": 388480.0,
      "text": "you want to do better for yourself and for your family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 388480.0,
      "end_time": 391680.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s sometimes hard to even know what those choices are"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 391680.0,
      "end_time": 393800.0,
      "text": "when you grow up in a community like I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 393800.0,
      "end_time": 395440.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 395440.0,
      "end_time": 398360.0,
      "text": "that you had to go to law school to be a lawyer."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 398360.0,
      "end_time": 402320.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know that elite universities, as research consistently tells us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 402320.0,
      "end_time": 404120.0,
      "text": "are cheaper for low-income kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 404120.0,
      "end_time": 406720.0,
      "text": "because these universities have bigger endowments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 406720.0,
      "end_time": 408920.0,
      "text": "can offer more generous financial aid."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 408920.0,
      "end_time": 410200.0,
      "text": "I remember I learned this"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 410200.0,
      "end_time": 413040.0,
      "text": "when I got the financial aid letter from Yale for myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 413040.0,
      "end_time": 415760.0,
      "text": "tens of thousands of dollars in need-based aid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 415760.0,
      "end_time": 417920.0,
      "text": "which is a term I had never heard before."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 417920.0,
      "end_time": 420600.0,
      "text": "But I turned to my aunt when I got that letter and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 420600.0,
      "end_time": 423920.0,
      "text": "&quot;You know, I think this just means that for the first time in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 423920.0,
      "end_time": 427360.0,
      "text": "being poor has paid really well.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 427360.0,
      "end_time": 430200.0,
      "text": "So I didn&#39;t have access to that information"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 430200.0,
      "end_time": 433880.0,
      "text": "because the social networks around me didn&#39;t have access to that information."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 433880.0,
      "end_time": 437560.0,
      "text": "I learned from my community how to shoot a gun, how to shoot it well."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 437560.0,
      "end_time": 440040.0,
      "text": "I learned how to make a damn good biscuit recipe."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 440040.0,
      "end_time": 444080.0,
      "text": "The trick, by the way, is frozen butter, not warm butter."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 444080.0,
      "end_time": 446000.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t learn how to get ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 446000.0,
      "end_time": 448600.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t learn how to make the good decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448600.0,
      "end_time": 450480.0,
      "text": "about education and opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 450480.0,
      "end_time": 453200.0,
      "text": "that you need to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 453200.0,
      "end_time": 456400.0,
      "text": "to actually have a chance in this 21st century knowledge economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 456400.0,
      "end_time": 460560.0,
      "text": "Economists call the value that we gain from our informal networks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 460560.0,
      "end_time": 464200.0,
      "text": "from our friends and colleagues and family &quot;social capital.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 464200.0,
      "end_time": 468040.0,
      "text": "The social capital that I had wasn&#39;t built for 21st century America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 468040.0,
      "end_time": 470360.0,
      "text": "and it showed."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 470360.0,
      "end_time": 473320.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s something else that&#39;s really important that&#39;s going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 473320.0,
      "end_time": 475520.0,
      "text": "that our community doesn&#39;t like to talk about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 475520.0,
      "end_time": 477120.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s very real."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 477120.0,
      "end_time": 479040.0,
      "text": "Working-class kids are much more likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 479040.0,
      "end_time": 481800.0,
      "text": "to face what&#39;s called adverse childhood experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 481800.0,
      "end_time": 486280.0,
      "text": "which is just a fancy word for childhood trauma:"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 486280.0,
      "end_time": 489880.0,
      "text": "getting hit or yelled at, put down by a parent repeatedly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 489880.0,
      "end_time": 492320.0,
      "text": "watching someone hit or beat your parent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 492320.0,
      "end_time": 495720.0,
      "text": "watching someone do drugs or abuse alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 495720.0,
      "end_time": 498280.0,
      "text": "These are all instances of childhood trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 498280.0,
      "end_time": 500960.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re pretty commonplace in my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 500960.0,
      "end_time": 504400.0,
      "text": "Importantly, they&#39;re not just commonplace in my family right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 504400.0,
      "end_time": 506440.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re also multigenerational."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 506440.0,
      "end_time": 508640.0,
      "text": "So my grandparents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 508640.0,
      "end_time": 511440.0,
      "text": "the very first time that they had kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 511440.0,
      "end_time": 514160.0,
      "text": "they expected that they were going to raise them in a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 514159.99999999994,
      "end_time": 515799.99999999994,
      "text": "that was uniquely good."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 515799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517079.99999999994,
      "text": "They were middle class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 517080.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519485.00000000006,
      "text": "they were able to earn a good wage in a steel mill."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 519485.0,
      "end_time": 520840.0,
      "text": "But what ended up happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 520840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523880.00000000006,
      "text": "is that they exposed their kids to a lot of the childhood trauma"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 523880.0,
      "end_time": 526600.0,
      "text": "that had gone back many generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 526600.0,
      "end_time": 532120.0,
      "text": "My mom was 12 when she saw my grandma set my grandfather on fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 532120.0,
      "end_time": 534960.0,
      "text": "His crime was that he came home drunk"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 534960.0,
      "end_time": 536200.0,
      "text": "after she told him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 536200.0,
      "end_time": 539240.0,
      "text": "&quot;If you come home drunk, I&#39;m gonna kill you.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 539240.0,
      "end_time": 541440.0,
      "text": "And she tried to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 541440.0,
      "end_time": 545520.0,
      "text": "Think about the way that that affects a child&#39;s mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 545520.0,
      "end_time": 548480.0,
      "text": "And we think of these things as especially rare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 548480.0,
      "end_time": 552480.0,
      "text": "but a study by the Wisconsin Children&#39;s Trust Fund found"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 552480.0,
      "end_time": 558800.0,
      "text": "that 40 percent of low-income kids face multiple instances of childhood trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 558800.0,
      "end_time": 562120.0,
      "text": "compared to only 29 percent for upper-income kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 562120.0,
      "end_time": 564800.0,
      "text": "And think about what that really means."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 564800.0,
      "end_time": 566560.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a low-income kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 566560.0,
      "end_time": 571040.0,
      "text": "almost half of you face multiple instances of childhood trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 571040.0,
      "end_time": 572880.0,
      "text": "This is not an isolated problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 572880.0,
      "end_time": 575800.0,
      "text": "This is a very significant issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 575800.0,
      "end_time": 579920.0,
      "text": "We know what happens to the kids who experience that life."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 579920.0,
      "end_time": 583240.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re more likely to do drugs, more likely to go to jail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 583240.0,
      "end_time": 585560.0,
      "text": "more likely to drop out of high school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 585560.0,
      "end_time": 587000.0,
      "text": "and most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 587000.0,
      "end_time": 589240.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re more likely to do to their children"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 589240.0,
      "end_time": 591640.0,
      "text": "what their parents did to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 591640.0,
      "end_time": 594760.0,
      "text": "This trauma, this chaos in the home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 594760.0,
      "end_time": 598240.0,
      "text": "is our culture&#39;s very worst gift to our children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 598240.0,
      "end_time": 602280.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a gift that keeps on giving."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 602280.0,
      "end_time": 604120.0,
      "text": "So you combine all that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 604120.0,
      "end_time": 606840.0,
      "text": "the hopelessness, the despair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 606840.0,
      "end_time": 609200.0,
      "text": "the cynicism about the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 609200.0,
      "end_time": 611440.0,
      "text": "the childhood trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 611440.0,
      "end_time": 613360.0,
      "text": "the low social capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 613360.0,
      "end_time": 615680.0,
      "text": "and you begin to understand why me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 615680.0,
      "end_time": 617280.0,
      "text": "at the age of 14,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 617280.0,
      "end_time": 619640.0,
      "text": "was ready to become just another statistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 619640.0,
      "end_time": 622640.0,
      "text": "another kid who failed to beat the odds."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 622640.0,
      "end_time": 625360.0,
      "text": "But something unexpected happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 625360.0,
      "end_time": 627120.0,
      "text": "I did beat the odds."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 627120.0,
      "end_time": 629280.0,
      "text": "Things turned up for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 629280.0,
      "end_time": 633040.0,
      "text": "I graduated from high school, from college, I went to law school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 633040.0,
      "end_time": 635320.0,
      "text": "and I have a pretty good job now."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 635320.0,
      "end_time": 637320.0,
      "text": "So what happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 637320.0,
      "end_time": 639880.0,
      "text": "Well, one thing that happened is that my grandparents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 639880.0,
      "end_time": 642440.0,
      "text": "the same grandparents of setting someone on fire fame,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 642440.0,
      "end_time": 645320.0,
      "text": "they really shaped up by the time I came around."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 645320.0,
      "end_time": 648400.0,
      "text": "They provided me a stable home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 648400.0,
      "end_time": 649720.0,
      "text": "a stable family."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 649720.0,
      "end_time": 650960.0,
      "text": "They made sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 650960.0,
      "end_time": 654120.0,
      "text": "that when my parents weren&#39;t able to do the things that kids need,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 654120.0,
      "end_time": 656880.0,
      "text": "they stepped in and filled that role."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 656880.0,
      "end_time": 659560.0,
      "text": "My grandma especially did two things that really matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 659560.0,
      "end_time": 663080.0,
      "text": "One, she provided that peaceful home that allowed me to focus on homework"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 663080.0,
      "end_time": 665720.0,
      "text": "and the things that kids should be focused on."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 665720.0,
      "end_time": 668120.0,
      "text": "But she was also this incredibly perceptive woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 668120.0,
      "end_time": 670520.0,
      "text": "despite not even having a middle school education."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 670520.0,
      "end_time": 673200.0,
      "text": "She recognized the message that my community had for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 673200.0,
      "end_time": 675280.0,
      "text": "that my choices didn&#39;t matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 675280.0,
      "end_time": 677120.0,
      "text": "that the deck was stacked against me."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 677120.0,
      "end_time": 678360.0,
      "text": "She once told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 678360.0,
      "end_time": 682360.0,
      "text": "&quot;JD, never be like those losers who think the deck is stacked against them."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 682360.0,
      "end_time": 684720.0,
      "text": "You can do anything you want to.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 684720.0,
      "end_time": 687960.0,
      "text": "And yet she recognized that life wasn&#39;t fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 687960.0,
      "end_time": 689600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to strike that balance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 689600.0,
      "end_time": 691640.0,
      "text": "to tell a kid that life isn&#39;t fair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 691640.0,
      "end_time": 696920.0,
      "text": "but also recognize and enforce in them the reality that their choices matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 696920.0,
      "end_time": 701040.0,
      "text": "But mamaw was able to strike that balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 701040.0,
      "end_time": 704360.0,
      "text": "The other thing that really helped was the United States Marine Corps."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 704360.0,
      "end_time": 707880.0,
      "text": "So we think of the Marine Corps as a military outfit, and of course it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 707880.0,
      "end_time": 710760.0,
      "text": "but for me, the US Marine Corps was a four-year crash course"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 710760.0,
      "end_time": 712000.0,
      "text": "in character education."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 712000.0,
      "end_time": 714400.0,
      "text": "It taught me how to make a bed, how to do laundry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 714400.0,
      "end_time": 716680.0,
      "text": "how to wake up early, how to manage my finances."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 716680.0,
      "end_time": 718880.0,
      "text": "These are things my community didn&#39;t teach me."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 718880.0,
      "end_time": 721857.0,
      "text": "I remember when I went to go buy a car for the very first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 721857.0,
      "end_time": 726200.0,
      "text": "I was offered a dealer&#39;s low, low interest rate of 21.9 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 726200.0,
      "end_time": 729680.0,
      "text": "and I was ready to sign on the dotted line."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 729680.0,
      "end_time": 731560.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t take that deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 731560.0,
      "end_time": 733600.0,
      "text": "because I went and took it to my officer"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 733600.0,
      "end_time": 735760.0,
      "text": "who told me, &quot;Stop being an idiot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 735760.0,
      "end_time": 738280.0,
      "text": "go to the local credit union, and get a better deal.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 738280.0,
      "end_time": 739760.0,
      "text": "And so that&#39;s what I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 739760.0,
      "end_time": 741200.0,
      "text": "But without the Marine Corps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 741200.0,
      "end_time": 743480.0,
      "text": "I would have never had access to that knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 743480.0,
      "end_time": 746720.0,
      "text": "I would have had a financial calamity, frankly."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 746720.0,
      "end_time": 749880.0,
      "text": "The last thing I want to say is that I had a lot of good fortune"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 749880.0,
      "end_time": 751480.0,
      "text": "in the mentors and people"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 751480.0,
      "end_time": 753640.0,
      "text": "who have played an important role in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 753640.0,
      "end_time": 756720.0,
      "text": "From the Marines, from Ohio State, from Yale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 756720.0,
      "end_time": 758000.0,
      "text": "from other places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 758000.0,
      "end_time": 759680.0,
      "text": "people have really stepped in"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 759680.0,
      "end_time": 762520.0,
      "text": "and ensured that they filled that social capital gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 762520.0,
      "end_time": 765480.0,
      "text": "that it was pretty obvious, apparently, that I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 765480.0,
      "end_time": 767840.0,
      "text": "That comes from good fortune,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 767840.0,
      "end_time": 771160.0,
      "text": "but a lot of children aren&#39;t going to have that good fortune,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 771160.0,
      "end_time": 774880.0,
      "text": "and I think that raises really important questions for all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 774880.0,
      "end_time": 777600.0,
      "text": "about how we&#39;re going to change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 777600.0,
      "end_time": 781600.0,
      "text": "We need to ask questions about how we&#39;re going to give low-income kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 781600.0,
      "end_time": 785160.0,
      "text": "who come from a broken home access to a loving home."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 785160.0,
      "end_time": 786440.0,
      "text": "We need to ask questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 786440.0,
      "end_time": 788800.0,
      "text": "about how we&#39;re going to teach low-income parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 788800.0,
      "end_time": 790960.0,
      "text": "how to better interact with their children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 790960.0,
      "end_time": 792480.0,
      "text": "with their partners."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 792480.0,
      "end_time": 796960.0,
      "text": "We need to ask questions about how we give social capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 796960.0,
      "end_time": 800360.0,
      "text": "mentorship to low-income kids who don&#39;t have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 800360.0,
      "end_time": 803440.0,
      "text": "We need to think about how we teach working class children"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 803440.0,
      "end_time": 805960.0,
      "text": "about not just hard skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 805960.0,
      "end_time": 808080.0,
      "text": "like reading, mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 808080.0,
      "end_time": 809440.0,
      "text": "but also soft skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 809440.0,
      "end_time": 813440.0,
      "text": "like conflict resolution and financial management."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 813440.0,
      "end_time": 816680.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t have all of the answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 816680.0,
      "end_time": 820360.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know all of the solutions to this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 820360.0,
      "end_time": 822600.0,
      "text": "but I do know this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 822600.0,
      "end_time": 824360.0,
      "text": "in southern Ohio right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 824360.0,
      "end_time": 828160.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a kid who is anxiously awaiting their dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 828160.0,
      "end_time": 830560.0,
      "text": "wondering whether, when he comes through the door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 830560.0,
      "end_time": 834000.0,
      "text": "he&#39;ll walk calmly or stumble drunkly."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 834000.0,
      "end_time": 836560.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a kid"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 836560.0,
      "end_time": 838920.0,
      "text": "whose mom sticks a needle in her arm"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 838920.0,
      "end_time": 840440.0,
      "text": "and passes out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 840440.0,
      "end_time": 843360.0,
      "text": "and he doesn&#39;t know why she doesn&#39;t cook him dinner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 843360.0,
      "end_time": 846400.0,
      "text": "and he goes to bed hungry that night."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 846400.0,
      "end_time": 850360.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a kid who has no hope for the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 850360.0,
      "end_time": 853640.0,
      "text": "but desperately wants to live a better life."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 853640.0,
      "end_time": 856680.0,
      "text": "They just want somebody to show it to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 856680.0,
      "end_time": 858560.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have all the answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 858560.0,
      "end_time": 863520.0,
      "text": "but I know that unless our society starts asking better questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 863520.0,
      "end_time": 865640.0,
      "text": "about why I was so lucky"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 865640.0,
      "end_time": 868720.0,
      "text": "and about how to get that luck to more of our communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 868720.0,
      "end_time": 870400.0,
      "text": "and our country&#39;s children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 870400.0,
      "end_time": 873680.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to continue to have a very significant problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 873680.0,
      "end_time": 874920.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 874920.0,
      "end_time": 884920.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}